quran[4{c,v,t}:
2,102,"aur lagey unn cheezon ki pairwi karne, jo shiyateen , sulaiman ki saltanat ka naam le kar paish kya karte thay, halaank sulaiman ne kabhi kufar nahi kya, kufar ke murtakib to woh shyatin thay jo logon ko jaadoo giri ki taleem dete thay woh peechay parre uss cheez ke jo babul mein do firshton, harwat o Maruat par nazil ki gayi thi, halaank woh ( farishtay ) jab bhi kisi ko is ki taleem dete thay, to pehlay saaf tor par mutnabba kar diya karte thay ke"" dekh, hum mehez aik azmaish hain, to kufar mein mubtala nah ho"" phir bhi yeh log unn se woh cheez sikhte thay, jis se shohar aur biwi mein judai daal den zahir tha ke azan Ellahi ke baghair woh is zariye se kisi ko bhi zarrar nah pouncha satke thay, mgras ke bawajood woh aisi cheez sikhte thay jo khud un ke liye naffa bakhash nahi, balkay nuqsaan daal hay thi aur inhen khoob maloom tha ke jo is cheez ka khredar bana, is ke liye akhirat mein koi hissa nahi kitni buri mata thi jis ke badlay unhon ne apni jaanun ko beech dala, kash inhen maloom hota !"
2,103,"agar woh imaan aur taqwa ikhtiyar karte, to Allah ke haan is ka jo badla milta, woh un ke liye ziyada behtar tha, kash unhen khabar hoti"
2,104,"ae logo jo imaan laaye ho : ra-ana nah kaha karo, balkay anzarna kaho aur tavajja se baat ko suno, yeh kafir to azaab alim ke mustahiq hain"
2,105,"yeh log jinhon ne dawat haq ko qubool karne se inkaar kar diya hai, khuwa ahal kitaab mein se hon ya mushriq hon, hargiz yeh pasand nahi karte ke tumahray Rab ki taraf se tum par koi bhalai nazil ho, magar Allah jis ko chahta hai, apni rehmat ke liye chunn laita hai aur woh bara fazl frmane wala hai"
